				<td colspan="2"><span>First of all, let's talk about backpieces.
<br />

<br />
I just got a silver bracelet of speed from the Doze quest, so I am now returning my CoF to my friend (who owns it).  I need a new backpiece.  I'm a HP freak (I just got to 4117hp unbuffed woot) so HP are a big thing for me... as are, of course, resists.
<br />

<br />
Secondly, helms.
<br />

<br />
I have a Velium Frostreaver's crown.  Ugh sums it up nicely.
<br />

<br />
But I have grown used to (and now rely on, really) the see invis and ultravision.  What should I be looking at to upgrade this?  Seemed like a lot of points to get the Takish helm and then aug it with see invis... so I dont like that idea much.  Ornate helms are fairly weak, though I've considered them.
<br />

<br />
http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=852635 to see my gear.
<br />

<br />
Our guild kills Tormax occasionally, so I've considered his crown, though my abysmal luck would have it that I've still NEVER attended a tormax raid, even though I've killed statue/AoW a billion times.
<br />

<br />
So thoughts?<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
